\c 7
\s AbaFarisi lababhali basolwa ngenxa yezimiso zabo
\p
\v 1 Kwasekubuthana kuye abaFarisi, labanye bababhali, ababevela eJerusalema\x + Mat. 15.1-28.\x*;
\v 2 sebebonile ukuthi abanye babafundi bakhe badla izinkwa ngezandla ezingcolileyo, okuyikuthi ezingagezwanga, basola.
\v 3 Ngoba abaFarisi lamaJuda bonke kabadli, ngaphandle kokuthi bagezisise izandla \add zabo\add*, belondoloza isiko labadala\x + 7.5. Mat. 15.20.\x*.
\v 4 Nxa \add be\add*vela emdangeni, kabadli, ngaphandle kokuthi bageze\x + 7.8. Heb. 9.10. Joha. 2.6.\x*; futhi zikhona ezinye izinto ezinengi abazemukelayo ukuzilondoloza, ukugezisa\x + 7.8. Heb. 9.10. Joha. 2.6.\x* inkezo lembiza lezitsha zethusi lemibheda\x + 7.8. Mat. 23.25. Luka 11.39.\x*.
\v 5 Emva kwalokhu abaFarisi lababhali bambuza bathi: Kungani abafundi bakho bengahambi ngesiko labadala, kodwa badla isinkwa ngezandla ezingahlanjwanga\x + 7.5. Mat. 15.20.\x*?
\p
\v 6 Kodwa waphendula wathi kubo: UIsaya waprofetha kuhle ngani lina bazenzisi, njengokulotshiweyo \add ukuthi\add*: Lesisizwe singidumisa ngezindebe, kodwa inhliziyo yabo ikhatshana lami\x + Isa. 29.13.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa zingikhonza ngeze, zifundisa izimfundiso \add eziy\add*imilayo yabantu.
\v 8 Ngoba liyekela umlayo kaNkulunkulu, ligcine isiko labantu, ukugezisa imbiza lenkezo\x + 7.4.\x*; lezinye izinto ezinengi ezinjalo liyazenza\x + 7.13.\x*.
\v 9 Wasesithi kubo: Liyachitha kuhle umlayo kaNkulunkulu, ukuze lilondoloze isiko lenu\x + 6.26. Luka 7.30; 10.16. Joha. 12.48. 1 Kor. 1.19. Gal. 3.15. 1 Thes. 4.8. 1 Tim. 5.12. Heb. 10.28. Juda 1.8.\x*.
\v 10 Ngoba uMozisi wathi: Hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko\x + Eks. 20.12.\x*; lokuthi: Othuka uyise kumbe unina kumele afe ukufa\x + Eks. 21.17.\x*;
\v 11 kodwa lina lithi: Aluba umuntu esithi kuyise kumbe kunina: Lokho obungasizwa yimi ngakho, "liKhobane", okuyikuthi umnikelo \add kuNkulunkulu\add*;
\v 12 kalisamvumeli ukwenzela uyise kumbe unina ulutho\x + Levi 1.2. Mat. 27.6. Mark. 5.41.\x*,
\v 13 lilenza ize ilizwi likaNkulunkulu ngesiko lenu eliliqhubayo; lezinto ezinengi ezinjalo liyazenza\x + 7.13.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Esebizile kuye ixuku lonke, wathi kilo: Ngilalelani lonke, liqedisise.
\v 15 Kalukho ulutho olungaphandle komuntu olungamngcolisa lungena kuye; kodwa izinto eziphuma kuye, yizo lezo ezingcolisa umuntu.
\v 16 Uba ekhona olendlebe zokuzwa akezwe\x + Mat. 11.15.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Esengenile endlini evela exukwini\x + 3.19.\x*, abafundi bakhe bambuza ngomfanekiso\x + Mat. 15.15.\x*.
\v 18 Wasesithi kubo: Ngokunjalo lani lingabangelakuqedisisa yini? Kaliqedisisi yini ukuthi konke okungaphandle okungena emuntwini kungemngcolise?
\v 19 Ngoba kakungeni enhliziyweni yakhe, kodwa esiswini, kuphumele ngaphandle, kuhlambulula ukudla konke.
\v 20 Wasesithi: Okuphumayo emuntwini, yikho okungcolisa umuntu.
\v 21 Ngoba kuphuma ngaphakathi enhliziyweni yabantu imicabango emibi, ukuphinga, ukufeba, ukubulala,
\v 22 ukweba, ubuhwaba\x + Roma 1.29.\x*\f + \fk ubuhwaba: \fl Gr. \fq ubuhwaba, inkohlakalo\f*, ukuxhwala\x + Roma 1.29.\x*, inkohliso, amanyala\x + 2 Kor. 12.21. Gal. 5.19. Efe. 4.19. 2 Pet. 2.7. Juda 1.4. Roma 13.13. 1 Pet. 4.3. 2 Pet. 2.18.\x*, ilihlo elibi\x + Mat. 6.23.\x*, inhlamba, ukuzigqaja\x + Roma 1.30.\x*, ubuthutha\x + 2 Kor. 11.1,17,21.\x*;
\v 23 zonke lezizinto ezimbi zivela ngaphakathi, zimngcolise umuntu.
\s Owesifazana weSirofenike
\p
\v 24 Wasesukuma lapho waya emikhawulweni yeTire leSidoni\x + Mat. 15.21.\x*. Wangena endlini, engathandi ukuthi kwaziwe muntu, kodwa wayengelakufihlakala.
\v 25 Ngoba owesifazana, olentombazana yakhe elomoya ongcolileyo, esezwile ngaye, weza wawa phansi enyaweni zakhe;
\v 26 njalo owesifazana wayengumGriki, engumSirofenike ngokuzalwa\x + Mat. 4.24. Mark. 7.24.\x*; wasemncenga ukuthi akhuphe idimoni endodakazini yakhe.
\v 27 Kodwa uJesu wathi kuye: Ake kusuthe abantwana kuqala; ngoba kakukuhle ukuthatha isinkwa sabantwana sisiphosele izinjana.
\v 28 Kodwa waphendula wathi kuye: Yebo, Nkosi; kodwa lezinjana ezingaphansi kwetafula ziyadla imvuthuluka yabantwana.
\v 29 Wasesithi kuye: Ngenxa yalokhukutsho hamba-ke; idimoni liphumile endodakazini yakho.
\v 30 Wasesuka waya endlini yakhe, wafica idimoni seliphumile, lendodakazi ilele embhedeni\x + Mat. 8.14.\x*.
\s Isacuthe esigagasayo siyasiliswa
\p
\v 31 Wasebuya wasuka\x + 7.31,32,37. Mat. 15.29-31.\x* emikhawulweni yeTire leSidoni\x + Mat. 15.21.\x*, weza elwandle lweGalili\x + Mat. 4.18.\x*, phakathi kwemikhawulo yeDikapolisi\x + Mat. 4.25.\x*.
\v 32 Basebeletha kuye isacuthe esigagasayo\x + Isa. 35.6.\x*, bamncenga ukuthi abeke isandla \add sakhe\add* phezu kwaso\x + Luka 13.13.\x*.
\v 33 Wasesikhupha exukwini \add saba\add*sodwa, wafaka iminwe yakhe endlebeni zaso\x + 8.23.\x*, wakhafula\x + 8.23. Joha. 9.6. 2 Kho. 2.21.\x* wathinta ulimi lwaso\x + Mat. 20.34.\x*,
\v 34 ekhangela phezulu ezulwini\x + Mat. 14.19. Mark. 6.41. Joha. 11.41; 17.1.\x*, wabubula\x + 8.12. Joha. 11.33,38.\x*, wathi kuso: "Efatha"; okuyikuthi: Vulwa\x + 5.41.\x*!
\v 35 Njalo zahle zavulwa indlebe zaso; yasithukululwa intambo yolimi lwaso, sasesikhuluma saqonda\x + Isa. 35.5,6. Mat. 11.5. Luka 1.64.\x*.
\v 36 Wasebalaya ukuthi bangatsheli muntu\x + 5.43.\x*; kodwa lanxa\x + Mat. 9.31.\x* wayebalayile kakhulu, kwang'khona bekumemezela ngamandla\x + 5.43.\x*.
\v 37 Basebemangala kakhulukazi sibili, bathi: Uzenzile kuhle izinto zonke; wenza kokubili izacuthe ukuthi zizwe, lezimungulu ukuthi zikhulume\x + 6.51; 10.26.\x*.